dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.; "Willamette meridian."; Public land (township, range, and section) grid.; Shows alienated land within the national forest boundary in color.; Ranches identified by family name.; Text (6 panels) and table of distances on verso.; Originally folded to 25 x 12 cm.|97 x 84 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:126,720|General Map Collection
